Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:02.27,Default,Okay? So that, I\Njust wanted to kind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.27,0:21:05.16,Default,of show you how blocks\Ncapture the local variables
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:07.36,Default,that are just outside\Ntheir scope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:10.51,Default,Now, we have another\Nproblem in here, in fact,
